Thanks! Also, since alot of OSX paths contain whitespaces, I had to modify the mark function like so:<p><pre><code>  function mark {
      mkdir -p $MARKPATH; ln -s &quot;$(pwd)&quot; $MARKPATH/$1
    }
</code></pre>
Disclaimer: I&#x27;m not very good at bash, perhaps there is a nicer solution to this problem?
